#Methods-Project
- Author: Tao Wang

### Outline of the  project

  - Part1. Replicating Krusell Smith 1998 paper,including consumption function and  wealth distribution.
  - Part2. Reformulating the original model under assumptions of heterogeneous information. Specifically, we assume agents cannot observe perfectly the macro state variable good or bad. Instead, following information-based  models are used. 
   - Part2.1. Benchmark case with private signals independently drawn for each invidiuals.
   - Part2.2. Signal-extraction by observing the aggregate unemployment rate and inferring the the macro state. 

 
  
